    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受房地产市场低迷影响，中国垃圾债券遭遇今年最长跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-junk-bonds-suffer-longest-slide-in-year-on-property-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的垃圾美元债券连续七天下跌，为 2023 年 8 月以来最长的下跌周期，此前疲软的房屋销售数据凸显了该国房地产市场低迷的加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-junk-bonds-suffer-longest-slide-in-year-on-property-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 03:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济放缓担忧加剧，全球债券收益率跌至两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/global-bond-yields-drop-to-two-year-low-as-slowdown-fears-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对主要经济体增长放缓的担忧和降息预期升温，本周全球债券收益率跌至两年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/global-bond-yields-drop-to-two-year-low-as-slowdown-fears-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 02:31:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行委员暗示仍有可能加息，日元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/boj-board-member-signals-rate-hike-is-on-table-if-outlook-met</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行委员中川顺子发表评论称，只要经济表现符合预期，日本央行将继续调整政策，这一言论推动日元升至今年最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/boj-board-member-signals-rate-hike-is-on-table-if-outlook-met</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:56:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯与支持加密货币的特朗普在辩论中发生冲突，比特币价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/bitcoin-dips-as-harris-and-pro-crypto-trump-lock-horns-in-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对美国总统大选民主党候选人卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 与共和党竞争对手唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 之间的辩论做出反应，比特币出现下跌，而特朗普对加密货币行业十分感兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/bitcoin-dips-as-harris-and-pro-crypto-trump-lock-horns-in-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:51:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马召回和大众裁员威胁加剧德国工业危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汽车制造商正陷入更深的危机，损害该国最重要行业的未来，宝马汽车公司警告称，利润将受到代价高昂的刹车问题的冲击，大众汽车公司则取消了员工三十年来享受的就业保障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
